---
// Signals Section (Compact Glass Panel)
---

<section id="signals" class="signals fade-in-up">
  <div class="sticky-header">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2 class="section-title">Signals</h2>
      <p>保持敏锐，持续输入</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="signals-panel liquid-glass">
    <div class="signal-col">
      <h3>Thinking</h3>
      <ul class="signal-list">
        <li><span>《Vibe Coding 改变的不是效率，而是接口》</span></li>
        <li><span>《从 prompt 到 directing：交互范式的转移》</span></li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="signal-col">
      <h3>Following</h3>
      <ul class="signal-list">
        <li><span>Acquired (Podcast)</span></li>
        <li><span>Lex Fridman (Podcast)</span></li>
        <li><span>Andrej Karpathy</span></li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="signal-col">
      <h3>Using</h3>
      <ul class="signal-list">
        <li><span>Cursor & Arc Browser</span></li>
        <li><span>Figma & Linear</span></li>
        <li><span>PyTorch & Astro</span></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .signals {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    position: relative;
  }

  .sticky-header {
    position: sticky;
    top: var(--header-height);
    z-index: 10;
    backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, var(--color-bg) 60%, transparent);
    margin: 0 calc(var(--space-md) * -1);
    padding: var(--space-md) var(--space-md) var(--space-lg);
  }

  .section-title {
    display: inline-block;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 4vw, 4rem);
  }

  .signals-panel {
    margin-top: var(--space-md);
    padding: var(--space-lg);
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-md);
  }

  .signal-col h3 {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
    font-size: 1rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  .signal-list {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.75rem;
  }

  .signal-list li {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
    transition: transform var(--transition-fast), color var(--transition-fast);
    cursor: default;
  }

  .signal-list li:hover {
    transform: translateX(8px);
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .signals-panel {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      padding: var(--space-md);
    }
  }
</style>
